body:
The queries in this section use the following index. This index
definition configures MongoDB Search to do the following:

- Automatically index all the dynamically indexable fields in the collection.

- Index the `products`, `funding_rounds`, and
  `funding_rounds.investments` fields as the [embeddedDocuments](bson-data-types-embedded-documents) type.

- Store the following fields on `mongot`:

  - `funding_rounds.raised_currency_code`

  - `funding_rounds.raised_amount`

  - `funding_rounds.investments`

  - `products.name`

```json
{
  "mappings": {
    "dynamic": true,
    "fields": {
      "funding_rounds": {
        "dynamic": true,
        "fields": {
          "investments": [
            {
              "dynamic": true,
              "type": "embeddedDocuments"
            }
          ]
        },
        "storedSource": {
          "include": [
            "raised_currency_code",
            "raised_amount",
            "investments"
          ]
        },
        "type": "embeddedDocuments"
      },
      "products": {
        "dynamic": true,
        "storedSource": {
          "include": [
            "name"
          ]
        },
        "type": "embeddedDocuments"
      }
    }
  }
}
```
